org.cloudgraph.hbase.io

Class TableWriterCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.io.WriterSupport
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.io.TableWriterCollector

  • public class TableWriterCollector
extends WriterSupport
    Traverses the change summary of the given Data Graph collecting a list of TableWriter elements with nested RowWriter elements. Each RowWriter represents the root of a new or existing Data Graph within the HBase table associated with the parent TableWriter.

    Graph nodes which are "unbound" (not assigned directly to a specific table) are assigned based on the first parent node within the graph. Other parent nodes (if exist) are ignored.

    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    CloudGraphConfig, TableConfig, TableWriter, RowWriter, commonj.sdo.ChangeSummary
